<p><strong>Small elemental, neutral evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 11</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 21 (6d6)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft., fly 30 ft.</p>

